      "comment": "TUSKEN WARRIOR (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 12 times for five wins and three minors. In the money last time at Capalaba (19.98) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2.5 lengths second. With a clean break looks hard to beat. LADY DREAMER (2) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (19.92) at this track. Must be included in calculations. OUTPLAYED (3) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 390m (22.01). Has a good record here at this journey. Unbeaten from this box in two starts. Expected to give a good account. REDEEMER'S WAY (6) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.",
